{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":403603,"duration_api_ms":397685,"num_turns":27,"result":"Implementation complete. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n**Milestone 2: Interactive Interview Agent**\n\n**Files created:**\n- `stages/plan_interview.sh` вҖ” `run_plan_interview()` that launches Claude in conversational mode with the template as context, handles Ctrl+C gracefully, and logs session metadata\n- `prompts/plan_interview.prompt.md` вҖ” System prompt template instructing the agent to interview one-question-at-a-time, write DESIGN.md progressively, use junior-friendly language, and enforce REQUIRED sections\n\n**Files modified:**\n- `lib/plan.sh` вҖ” Added config defaults (`PLAN_INTERVIEW_MODEL=sonnet`, `PLAN_INTERVIEW_MAX_TURNS=50`), wired `run_plan_interview()` into `run_plan()`, removed redundant output (M1 non-blocking note)\n- `tekhton.sh` вҖ” `--plan` block now sources `lib/prompts.sh` and `stages/plan_interview.sh`\n\n**Acceptance criteria met:**\n- Interview agent receives template content as context (via `{{TEMPLATE_CONTENT}}` in rendered prompt)\n- Agent asks one question at a time (enforced by system prompt rules)\n- Agent writes DESIGN.md progressively (instructed to write complete file after each answer)\n- Conversation is logged to `.claude/logs/` (session metadata + system prompt)\n- Ctrl+C preserves partial DESIGN.md (INT trap + progressive writes)\n\n**Validation:** All 20 tests pass, shellcheck clean (only pre-existing SC2034/SC1091 patterns).","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"f2e06d7a-2e10-4531-bb2b-723ab8485853","total_cost_usd":1.5128235000000003,"usage":{"input_tokens":21,"cache_creation_input_tokens":66916,"cache_read_input_tokens":1123787,"output_tokens":21304,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":66916,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage