{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":213729,"duration_api_ms":213213,"num_turns":11,"result":"`REVIEWER_REPORT.md` is written. Here's a summary of the review:\n\n---\n\n**Verdict: CHANGES_REQUIRED**\n\n**One simple blocker found:**\n\nThe `--plan` block in `tekhton.sh` calls `run_plan` bare. When the user presses Ctrl+C during the interview before any DESIGN.md is written, `run_plan_interview` returns 1, `run_plan` propagates it, and `set -euo pipefail` triggers `_tekhton_cleanup()` вҖ” printing the \"PIPELINE CRASHED\" banner. The fix is a one-liner: `run_plan || true`.\n\nThe `set -euo pipefail` absence in sourced files was confirmed by the M1 review as the established project convention (inherited from the entry point), so that is not a blocker here.\n\n**Non-blocking notes:**\n- `wc -l` leading-whitespace portability (cosmetic)\n- `--dangerously-skip-permissions` should be surfaced to the user with a brief `warn` before the session starts\n- Prompt's relative-path DESIGN.md assumption is implicit coupling worth documenting","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"1049f2ed-06fc-4022-9e7c-4e316f0c4696","total_cost_usd":0.63743675,"usage":{"input_tokens":9,"cache_creation_input_tokens":41119,"cache_read_input_tokens":230096,"output_tokens":10614,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":41119,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":9,"outputTokens":10614,"cacheReadInputTokens":230096,"cacheCreationInputTokens":41119,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.63743675,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"98b8d5fd-1dcf-4bce-a798-3dd32692ca3d"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":18876,"duration_api_ms":18279,"num_turns":8,"result":"## Done\n\nI've fixed the single blocker from the reviewer report:\n\n**Blocker fixed:**\n- **tekhton.sh line 175**: Changed `run_plan` to `run_plan || true` to prevent the crash diagnostic from triggering when users interrupt the interactive interview. This ensures non-zero exits from the planning flow don't falsely report a pipeline crash.\n\n**Files modified:** `tekhton.sh`\n\n**Verification:**\n- вң… `bash -n` syntax check passed\n- вң… No new shellcheck violations\n\nSummary written to `JR_CODER_SUMMARY.md`.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"6aa4c23d-2b21-4548-9d64-98fa0ad110b8","total_cost_usd":0.04033855,"usage":{"input_tokens":50,"cache_creation_input_tokens":11347,"cache_read_input_tokens":159248,"output_tokens":2036,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":11347,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-haiku-4-5":{"inputTokens":50,"outputTokens":2036,"cacheReadInputTokens":159248,"cacheCreationInputTokens":11347,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.04033855,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"a8a3e348-9d54-43d2-97e7-56b42e8f1acd"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":77307,"duration_api_ms":77024,"num_turns":9,"result":"**REVIEWER_REPORT.md written. Verdict: APPROVED_WITH_NOTES**\n\n**Cycle 1 blocker вҖ” VERIFIED FIXED:** `tekhton.sh:175` is now `run_plan || true`. The crash diagnostic no longer fires on user interruption of the planning flow.\n\n**No regressions introduced.** The fix was minimal and correct вҖ” a single `|| true` appended to the `run_plan` call in the `--plan` early-exit block.\n\n**Non-blocking notes carried forward from cycle 1** (none escalated to blockers since none are regressions from the cycle 2 rework):\n- Missing `set -euo pipefail` headers in `plan_interview.sh` and `lib/plan.sh` вҖ” sourced files inherit from `tekhton.sh`, so no runtime issue, but inconsistent with CLAUDE.md rule #2. Flagged for Milestone 7 cleanup.\n- `wc -l` whitespace portability in `plan_interview.sh`.\n- `--dangerously-skip-permissions` user-facing warning suggestion.\n- Implicit CWD coupling in the prompt template.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"32ec34ba-676f-4e75-9bbb-4ea89ec546a6","total_cost_usd":0.34792475,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":33925,"cache_read_input_tokens":96277,"output_tokens":3509,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":33925,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":6,"outputTokens":3509,"cacheReadInputTokens":96277,"cacheCreationInputTokens":33925,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.34792475,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"8a03f07e-3bed-4ae4-a88c-e6eca500a9e1"}
